title: Husky Liners “The River” - GearBox Product Features (:30)
description: Meet Paul Conklin. he is an avid fly-fisherman and his truck is always full of gear. Whether you’re looking to get more organized and keep your stuff from sliding around, or you’re the type that just wants an easy spot to hide all your garbage, the durable Husky Liners® GearBox® keeps you looking clean and organized.
